{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/6861265.Arnaldur_Indri_ason", "name": "Arnaldur Indri\u00f0ason", "birthDate": "1961-01-28 00:00:00", "genres": ["Crime", "Mystery", "Thriller"], "avgRating": 3.8, "reviewsCount": 13300, "ratingsCount": 159201, "about": "Arnaldur Indri\u00f0ason has the rare distinction of having won the Nordic Crime Novel Prize two years running. He is also the winner of the highly respected and world famous CWA Gold Dagger Award for the top crime novel of the year in the English language, Silence of the Grave. Arnaldur\u2019s novels have sold over 14 million copies worldwide, in 40 languages, and have won numerous well-respected prizes and received rave reviews all over the world."}
