d with his Osnabr\u00fcck background and speaking thematically of a critical examination of German history, whereby the preservation of human dignity and humanity in times of oppression, terror and war always was at the forefront of his literary creation. AKA:\u0388\u03c1\u03b9\u03c7 \u039c\u03b1\u03c1\u03af\u03b1 \u03a1\u03b5\u03bc\u03ac\u03c1\u03ba (Greek)\u042d\u0440\u0438\u0445 \u041c\u0430\u0440\u0438\u044f \u0420\u0435\u043c\u0430\u0440\u043a (Russian) ...more"}
{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/493232.Paolo_Giordano", "name": "Paolo Giordano", "birthDate": "1982-12-19 00:00:00", "avgRating": 3.64, "reviewsCount": 8227, "ratingsCount": 97294, "about": "Librarian Note: There is more than one author in the GoodReads database with this name. Paolo Giordano is a professional physicist and is currently working on a doctorate in particle physics. The Solitude of Prime Numbers, his first novel, took Italy by storm where it has sold over a million copies. It is being translated into twenty languages and has sold all over the world."}
